parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks and excessive consumption can lead to engine damage, premature wear, and potentially cause engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: burning a quart of oil every 850+ miles
smoke coming out of the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine performance issues, such as skipping, surging, and stalling, can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
Timing belt failure can cause engine damage, valve bending, and engine shutdown, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Failure of these critical components can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
Transmission failure can cause loss of vehicle speed, difficulty shifting gears, and grinding noises, which can lead to accidents, strand the driver, and result in costly repairs.
symptoms: transmission failure to engage or disengage

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter motor can cause the vehicle to fail to start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks, especially if the vehicle stalls in traffic.
symptoms: The starter motor fails to turn the engine
the ignition key must be turned off and on repeatedly to get the vehicle to start
the starter motor produces a clicking sound but the engine does not turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure (Turn Signal and Lighting Issues)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the lights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The headlights and interior lights extinguish when the turn signal is applied
the lights short out when turning right
the gearshift indicator light in the dashboard fails to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling due to Faulty Computer Chip
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the computer chip can cause the engine to stall, leading to loss of vehicle control and potential accidents.
symptoms: the engine shuts off without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
